Section 4: Coding Tasks

Example 4.1

User

Write a Python async URL fetcher.
AI Response
import asyncio, aiohttp

async def fetch(url):
async with aiohttp.ClientSession() as s:
async with s.get(url) as r:
return await r.text()

result = asyncio.run(fetch("https://example.com"))

Example 4.2

User

Write a Bash script to back up a directory.
AI Response
#!/bin/bash
SRC=$1; DST=$2; TS=$(date +%Y%m%d_%H%M%S)
tar -czf "$DST/backup_$TS.tar.gz" "$SRC"
echo "Backup done: $DST/backup_$TS.tar.gz"

Example 4.3

User

Write a deep clone function in JavaScript.
AI Response
function deepClone(obj) {
if (obj === null || typeof obj !== "object") return obj;
if (Array.isArray(obj)) return obj.map(deepClone);
return Object.fromEntries(
Object.entries(obj).map(([k,v]) => [k, deepClone(v)])
);
}

